      <title>贝莱德的雅各布斯：比特币 ETF 着眼于长期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-01-11/blackrock-s-jacobs-bitcoin-etf-focused-on-the-long-term-video</link>
