      <title>欧洲央行行长武伊西奇赞成降息开始后降息四分之一个百分点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/ecb-s-vujcic-favors-quarter-point-moves-once-rate-cuts-start</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行管理委员会成员鲍里斯·武伊契奇表示，他更倾向于在货币宽松开始后将借贷成本降低四分之一个百分点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/ecb-s-vujcic-favors-quarter-point-moves-once-rate-cuts-start</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 15:07:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Blackstone 任命联席首席信息官并任命新的房地产主管</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/blackstone-names-co-cios-elevates-new-head-of-real-estate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[黑石公司 (Blackstone Inc.) 正在为其庞大的房地产业务提拔一位新领导者，并任命两名投资主管担任公司高层，以加强这家全球最大另类投资管理公司的协调。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/blackstone-names-co-cios-elevates-new-head-of-real-estate</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 14:07:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>消费者物价指数 (CPI) 大幅波动，债券市场坚持降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/treasury-yields-rise-after-inflation-readings-trim-rate-cut-odds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[债券交易员对美联储将在未来几个月开始降息充满信心，基本上没有理会 12 月份高于预期的通胀数据。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/treasury-yields-rise-after-inflation-readings-trim-rate-cut-odds</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 14:04:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加纳获得债务减免条款，足以为国际货币基金组织释放 6 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/ghana-gets-debt-relief-terms-enough-to-unlock-imf-600-million</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加纳财政部长肯·奥弗里-阿塔 (Ken Ofori-Atta) 表示，加纳已收到官方债权人提供的债务减免条款清单草案，该草案足以让国际货币基金组织向这个西非国家支付 6 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/ghana-gets-debt-relief-terms-enough-to-unlock-imf-600-million</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 13:33:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Vonovia 获得 33 亿英镑第一笔英镑债券订单</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/vonovia-gets-3-5-billion-in-orders-for-first-stirling-bond-sale</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国房东 Vonovia SE 在欧洲一级市场获得了近 33 亿英镑（合 42 亿美元）的 4 亿英镑债券订单，延续了该地区一周以来最高的销售量。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/vonovia-gets-3-5-billion-in-orders-for-first-stirling-bond-sale</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 13:20:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
