      <title>热门消费者物价指数数据公布后，随着债券波动，股市下跌：市场总结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-10/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华尔街股市波动较大，通胀数据超出预期，削弱了对美联储 3 月份降息的押注，股市下跌，债券也难以寻找方向。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-10/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 22:43:58 GMT</pubDate>
